## 3. Database Schema (with Relationships)

### 3.1 Entity Relationship Diagram

```mermaid
erDiagram
    User ||--o{ WorkspaceMember : "belongs_to"
    User ||--o{ ProjectMember : "joined_as"
    User ||--o{ Task : "assigned_to"
    User ||--o{ Comment : "authored"
    User ||--o{ Workspace : "owns"

    Workspace ||--o{ WorkspaceMember : "has_members"
    Workspace ||--o{ Project : "contains"

    Project ||--o{ ProjectMember : "has_members"
    Project ||--o{ Task : "contains"

    Task ||--o{ Comment : "has_comments"
```

### 3.2 Complete Prisma Schema

```prisma
// ─── Enums ───────────────────────────────────────────────
enum ProjectStatus {
  PLANNING
  ACTIVE
  ON_HOLD
  COMPLETED
  CANCELLED
}

enum Priority {
  LOW
  MEDIUM
  HIGH
  URGENT
}

enum TaskStatus {
  TODO
  IN_PROGRESS
  DONE
  CANCELLED
}

enum TaskType {
  TASK
  BUG
  FEATURE
  IMPROVEMENT
  OTHER
}

enum MemberRole {
  ADMIN
  MEMBER
}

// ─── Models ──────────────────────────────────────────────
model User {
  id              String            @id                    // Clerk user ID
  name            String?
  email           String            @unique
  image           String?
  createdAt       DateTime          @default(now())
  updatedAt       DateTime          @updatedAt

  workspaces      WorkspaceMember[]
  ownedWorkspaces Workspace[]       @relation("WorkspaceOwner")
  projects        ProjectMember[]
  tasks           Task[]            @relation("TaskAssignee")
  comments        Comment[]
}

model Workspace {
  id          String            @id                        // Clerk org ID
  name        String
  slug        String            @unique
  description String?
  imageUrl    String?
  settings    Json              @default("{}")
  ownerId     String
  createdAt   DateTime          @default(now())
  updatedAt   DateTime          @updatedAt

  owner       User              @relation("WorkspaceOwner", fields: [ownerId], references: [id])
  members     WorkspaceMember[]
  projects    Project[]
}

model WorkspaceMember {
  id          String            @id @default(cuid())
  userId      String
  workspaceId String
  role        MemberRole        @default(MEMBER)
  message     String?

  user        User              @relation(fields: [userId], references: [id], onDelete: Cascade)
  workspace   Workspace         @relation(fields: [workspaceId], references: [id], onDelete: Cascade)

  @@unique([userId, workspaceId])
}

model Project {
  id          String            @id @default(cuid())
  workspaceId String
  name        String
  description String?
  status      ProjectStatus     @default(PLANNING)
  priority    Priority          @default(MEDIUM)
  progress    Int               @default(0)
  teamLead    String?                                     // User ID of team lead
  startDate   DateTime?
  endDate     DateTime?
  createdAt   DateTime          @default(now())
  updatedAt   DateTime          @updatedAt

  workspace   Workspace         @relation(fields: [workspaceId], references: [id], onDelete: Cascade)
  owner       User?             @relation(fields: [teamLead], references: [id])
  members     ProjectMember[]
  tasks       Task[]
}

model ProjectMember {
  id        String    @id @default(cuid())
  userId    String
  projectId String

  user      User      @relation(fields: [userId], references: [id], onDelete: Cascade)
  project   Project   @relation(fields: [projectId], references: [id], onDelete: Cascade)

  @@unique([userId, projectId])
}

model Task {
  id          String      @id @default(cuid())
  projectId   String
  title       String
  description String?
  type        TaskType    @default(TASK)
  status      TaskStatus  @default(TODO)
  priority    Priority    @default(MEDIUM)
  assigneeId  String?
  dueDate     DateTime?
  createdAt   DateTime    @default(now())
  updatedAt   DateTime    @updatedAt

  project     Project     @relation(fields: [projectId], references: [id], onDelete: Cascade)
  assignee    User?       @relation("TaskAssignee", fields: [assigneeId], references: [id])
  comments    Comment[]
}

model Comment {
  id        String    @id @default(cuid())
  taskId    String
  userId    String
  content   String
  createdAt DateTime  @default(now())

  task      Task      @relation(fields: [taskId], references: [id], onDelete: Cascade)
  user      User      @relation(fields: [userId], references: [id], onDelete: Cascade)
}
```

### 3.3 Key Relationships Summary

| Relationship | Type | Constraint |
|:-------------|:-----|:-----------|
| User ↔ Workspace | Many-to-Many (via WorkspaceMember) | `@@unique([userId, workspaceId])` |
| User ↔ Project | Many-to-Many (via ProjectMember) | `@@unique([userId, projectId])` |
| User → Task | One-to-Many (assignee) | Optional foreign key |
| Project → Task | One-to-Many | Cascade delete |
| Task → Comment | One-to-Many | Cascade delete |
| Workspace → Project | One-to-Many | Cascade delete |

---

## 4. API Endpoints (Request/Response)

### 4.1 Authentication

All protected routes require:
```
Headers: { Authorization: "Bearer <clerk_jwt_token>" }
```

The `protect` middleware extracts `userId` via `req.auth()` (Clerk SDK). Returns `401 Unauthorized` if no valid token.

### 4.2 Workspace APIs

| Method | Endpoint | Description | Auth |
|:-------|:---------|:------------|:-----|
| `GET` | `/api/workspaces` | Get all workspaces for logged-in user | ✅ |
| `POST` | `/api/workspaces/add-member` | Add member to workspace | ✅ Admin |

#### `GET /api/workspaces`

```json
// Response 200
[
  {
    "id": "org_abc123",
    "name": "GreatStack Dev",
    "slug": "greatstack-dev",
    "imageUrl": "https://...",
    "owner": { "id": "user_1", "name": "Harshit", "email": "..." },
    "members": [
      {
        "id": "wm_1",
        "userId": "user_1",
        "role": "ADMIN",
        "user": { "id": "user_1", "name": "Harshit", "email": "...", "image": "..." }
      }
    ],
    "projects": [
      {
        "id": "proj_1",
        "name": "Launchpad CRM",
        "status": "ACTIVE",
        "tasks": [
          {
            "id": "task_1",
            "title": "UI/UX Design",
            "assignee": { "id": "user_2", "name": "...", "email": "..." },
            "comments": [
              { "id": "com_1", "content": "Working on it", "user": { "name": "..." } }
            ]
          }
        ],
        "members": [{ "user": { "name": "...", "email": "..." } }],
        "owner": { "name": "..." }
      }
    ]
  }
]
```

#### `POST /api/workspaces/add-member`

```json
// Request Body
{
  "email": "user@example.com",
  "role": "MEMBER",           // "ADMIN" | "MEMBER"
  "workspaceId": "org_abc123",
  "message": "Welcome to the team!"
}

// Response 200
{
  "member": { "id": "wm_2", "userId": "user_2", "workspaceId": "org_abc123", "role": "MEMBER" },
  "message": "Member added successfully"
}

// Error Responses
// 404: { "message": "User not found" }
// 404: { "message": "Workspace not found" }
// 400: { "message": "Missing required parameters" }
// 400: { "message": "Invalid role" }
// 400: { "message": "User is already a member" }
// 401: { "message": "You don't have admin privileges" }
```

### 4.3 Project APIs

| Method | Endpoint | Description | Auth |
|:-------|:---------|:------------|:-----|
| `POST` | `/api/projects` | Create new project | ✅ Admin |
| `PUT` | `/api/projects` | Update project details | ✅ Admin/Lead |
| `POST` | `/api/projects/:projectId/add-member` | Add member to project | ✅ Lead |

#### `POST /api/projects`

```json
// Request Body
{
  "workspaceId": "org_abc123",
  "name": "Launchpad CRM",
  "description": "CRM application project",
  "status": "ACTIVE",
  "priority": "MEDIUM",
  "progress": 0,
  "teamLead": "user@example.com",    // Email of team lead
  "teamMembers": ["a@ex.com", "b@ex.com"],
  "startDate": "2026-03-25",
  "endDate": "2026-04-30"
}

// Response 200
{
  "project": {
    "id": "proj_1",
    "name": "Launchpad CRM",
    "members": [{ "user": { "name": "...", "email": "..." } }],
    "tasks": [],
    "owner": { "name": "..." }
  },
  "message": "Project created successfully"
}

// Error Responses
// 404: { "message": "Workspace not found" }
// 403: { "message": "You don't have permission to create project in this workspace" }
```

#### `PUT /api/projects`

```json
// Request Body (partial update)
{
  "id": "proj_1",
  "workspaceId": "org_abc123",
  "name": "Updated Name",
  "description": "Updated description",
  "status": "ACTIVE",
  "priority": "HIGH",
  "progress": 45,
  "startDate": "2026-03-25",
  "endDate": "2026-05-15"
}

// Response 200
{ "project": { ... }, "message": "Project updated successfully" }
```

#### `POST /api/projects/:projectId/add-member`

```json
// Request Body
{ "email": "newmember@example.com" }

// Response 200
{ "member": { "id": "pm_1", "userId": "...", "projectId": "..." }, "message": "Member added successfully" }
```

### 4.4 Task APIs

| Method | Endpoint | Description | Auth |
|:-------|:---------|:------------|:-----|
| `POST` | `/api/tasks` | Create new task | ✅ Lead |
| `PUT` | `/api/tasks/:id` | Update task (status, etc.) | ✅ Lead |
| `POST` | `/api/tasks/delete` | Bulk delete tasks | ✅ Lead |

#### `POST /api/tasks`

```json
// Request Body
{
  "projectId": "proj_1",
  "title": "Build Login Page",
  "description": "Implement login with OAuth",
  "type": "FEATURE",           // TASK | BUG | FEATURE | IMPROVEMENT | OTHER
  "status": "TODO",            // TODO | IN_PROGRESS | DONE | CANCELLED
  "priority": "HIGH",          // LOW | MEDIUM | HIGH | URGENT
  "assigneeId": "user_2",
  "dueDate": "2026-04-10"
}

// Response 200
{
  "task": {
    "id": "task_1",
    "title": "Build Login Page",
    "assignee": { "id": "user_2", "name": "...", "email": "..." },
    ...
  },
  "message": "Task created successfully"
}

// Side Effect: Triggers Inngest event "app/task.assigned" → sends email to assignee
```

#### `PUT /api/tasks/:id`

```json
// Request Body (any task fields)
{ "status": "DONE" }

// Response 200
{ "task": { ... }, "message": "Task updated successfully" }
```

#### `POST /api/tasks/delete`

```json
// Request Body
{ "taskIds": ["task_1", "task_2"] }

// Response 200
{ "message": "Task deleted successfully" }
```

### 4.5 Comment APIs

| Method | Endpoint | Description | Auth |
|:-------|:---------|:------------|:-----|
| `POST` | `/api/comments` | Add comment to task | ✅ Project Member |
| `GET` | `/api/comments/:taskId` | Get all comments for task | ✅ |

#### `POST /api/comments`

```json
// Request Body
{ "taskId": "task_1", "content": "I am working on it" }

// Response 200
{
  "id": "com_1",
  "taskId": "task_1",
  "content": "I am working on it",
  "userId": "user_1",
  "user": { "id": "user_1", "name": "Harshit", "image": "..." },
  "createdAt": "2026-03-25T..."
}
```

#### `GET /api/comments/:taskId`

```json
// Response 200
{
  "comments": [
    {
      "id": "com_1",
      "content": "I am working on it",
      "createdAt": "...",
      "user": { "id": "user_1", "name": "Harshit", "image": "..." }
    }
  ]
}
```

### 4.6 Inngest Webhook Endpoints (Internal)

| Event Name | Trigger | Action |
|:-----------|:--------|:-------|
| `clerk/user.created` | Clerk webhook | Save user to DB |
| `clerk/user.updated` | Clerk webhook | Update user in DB |
| `clerk/user.deleted` | Clerk webhook | Delete user from DB |
| `clerk/organization.created` | Clerk webhook | Save workspace + creator as ADMIN |
| `clerk/organization.updated` | Clerk webhook | Update workspace name/slug/image |
| `clerk/organization.deleted` | Clerk webhook | Delete workspace from DB |
| `clerk/organizationInvitation.accepted` | Clerk webhook | Add new workspace member |
| `app/task.assigned` | Task creation API | Send assignment email + schedule reminder |

